&lt;p&gt;Impact.com is growing quickly in the Nordics, Spain and France and now the Studio team, the in-house influencer marketing team, are looking to expand with a person focusing on influencer campaigns and support in Europe as well as the Nordics.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
